[MOD] core

// Trying to DROP the fabricated env var also fails. A native call needs no
// external config, but the [SRV] format requires an env-var list, so you cannot
// express a config-free local boundary at all today.
//
//   rune check cases/sidecar-no-env.rune --root .
//
[SRV] (SIDECAR)fs:
    local filesystem via native Deno APIs (Deno.writeTextFile / readFile)
    @docs https://docs.deno.com/api/deno/~/Deno.writeTextFile
